This is how to find_max of words:
  Remember that best is item 0 in words
  Remember that i is 1
  Do this words's length times:
    When i is at least words's length, then:
      Leave the loop
    End when
    When best is less than item i in words, then:
      Remember that best is item i in words
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is best
